1. *Velikom* brzinom je ulazio u sobu. (He entered the room with great speed.)
2. Ona je ponosno koračala *velikom* samopouzdanjem. (She walked proudly with great confidence.)
3. *Velikom* je poteškoćom uspela da postane najbolja. (She managed to become the best with great difficulty.)
4. On je dobio *veliko* priznanje. (He received great recognition.)
5. *Velikom* je radošću prihvatila njegovu ponudu. (She accepted his offer with great joy.)
6. *Velikom* je pažnjom pratio njenu priču. (He listened to her story with great attention.)